I. Setup Django Envoironment
============================
1. Install Python
2. python3 --version  
3. Setup virtual Env and Activate it
    python3 -m venv .venv   
    . .venv/scripts/activiate  

4. Install Django
    pip install django 

5. Install DB Client
    python -m pip install mysqlclient

6. Install pytest
    pip install pytest

5. Install DjangoRestFramework
    pip install djangorestframework

6. Create a Django project
    django-admin startproject CrossCheck . 

7. Start the Server
    python manage.py runserver

8. Create user/Password for the Django UI
    python manage.py createsuperuser

9. Change Password of a user
    python manage.py changepassword <user_name>

10. Create Migration Scripts for the Models
     python manage.py makemigrations CrossCheck

11. Apply Migration
     python manage.py migrate  
